3492284bc92896451c4e543e46ceed09e1a7b16ab982bc2ba08e956d078b14b8200af7a4560ae7e920e55550daa38b3a95f7415d77efff3f92d2b8d7adaabe33  0001-support-kwin-5.20.90.patch"
